ssion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If there are no stored API credentials, the refresh token will be exchaged for a new set of API credentials."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"New or renewed API credentials will be automatically stored in the Keychain. "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This method is thread-safe"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Usage","anchor":"Usage"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["credentialsManager.apiCredentials(forAudience: \"http:\/\/example.com\/api\") { result in","    switch result {","    case .success(let apiCredentials):","        print(\"Obtained API credentials: \\(apiCredentials)\")","    case .failure(let error):","        print(\"Failed with: \\(error)\")","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default scopes configured for the API will be granted if you don’t request any specific scopes. If you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"request different scopes than the ones that were granted last time, the API credentials will be renewed"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"immediately, regardless of whether they are expired or not."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["credentialsManager.apiCredentials(forAudience: \"http:\/\/example.com\/api\",","                                  scope: \"read:todos update:todos\") { print($0) }"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To avoid retrieving access tokens with too little time left, enforce a minimum TTL (in seconds):"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["credentialsManager.apiCredentials(forAudience: \"http:\/\/example.com\/api\",","                                  minTTL: 60) { print($0) }"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can specify custom parameters or headers for the exchange reque